 domain-invariant linguistic structures and entity semantics, it also improves fluency and coherence over existing CDDA methods. The resulting system would adaptively balance reliance on learned patterns versus enriched context, enabling efficient, interpretable, and generalizable NED across diverse domains such as biomedical texts, social media, and legal documents.

